# Group Topics
Ações relacionadas aos topicos
## Posts de um tópico [/tag/{id}/posts?limit={limit}]
### Get Posts [GET]

Solicita os posts de uma tag

+ Parameters
    + id: 2 (required, Number) - Id of tag.
    + limit: 4 (optional, Number) - Limit number of articles
        + Default: 4

+ Request (application/json)
    + Headers
    
            Authorization: user_key_auth (required, String) - Key authorization

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body

